				trigger:'<span class="symbol mask"/><span class="symbol crow"/><b>Question Loyalty</b>: After succeeding, the target gains the following Condition for the rest of the round: “Whose Side Am I On?!: Anyone attacking this character gains a <span class="symbol plus"/> to the flip.”',
				limit:'',
